1
00:00:29,620 --> 00:00:32,980
=The Secret of the Lost Pearl=

2
00:00:33,020 --> 00:00:34,940
=Episode 24=
(Fiction. Do not imitate.)

3
00:01:31,160 --> 00:01:32,000
The Princess!

4
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:32,840
Let's go!

5
00:01:50,590 --> 00:01:51,760
Your Highness!

6
00:01:51,950 --> 00:01:52,790
Oh, no!

7
00:01:52,790 --> 00:01:54,200
- Your Highness!
- Hide me!

8
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,790
- Your Highness!
- Your Highness!

9
00:01:55,790 --> 00:01:57,710
Go find her!

10
00:01:57,710 --> 00:01:59,310
Your Highness!

11
00:01:59,510 --> 00:02:01,790
Your Highness, where are you?

12
00:02:02,430 --> 00:02:04,150
Come out, Your Highness!

13
00:02:04,150 --> 00:02:05,870
- Your Highness!
- Your Highness!

14
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:09,080
Go find her!

15
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,870
You are the princess?

16
00:02:11,470 --> 00:02:13,120
Yes, I'm Princess Xian'an.

17
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:14,200
And you?

18
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:18,630
I am Bai Yao, son of Bai Shiyuan,
Director of the Ministry of Works.

19
00:02:18,630 --> 00:02:19,520
Where are you?

20
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:21,280
Where exactly are you?

21
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,120
Thank you.

22
00:02:23,590 --> 00:02:25,630
Your kick was really accurate.

23
00:02:26,030 --> 00:02:27,310
Let's play another day.

24
00:02:27,410 --> 00:02:28,280
Sure!

25
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:30,080
- Your Highness!
- Your Highness!

26
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,840
- You're here!
- I'll leave first.

27
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:34,960
Your Highness!

28
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,240
- Don't run
- Hurry!

29
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,590
- Hurry!
- Your Highness!

30
00:02:37,590 --> 00:02:39,190
Your Highness, stop!

31
00:02:39,190 --> 00:02:40,360
Where are you going?

32
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,870
Your Highness, slow down!

33
00:02:42,910 --> 00:02:44,150
Your Highness!

34
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,680
Where are you going?

35
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,493
What are you looking at?

36
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,240
Your Highness!

37
00:03:12,590 --> 00:03:14,080
The 10th Hui glissando to the 9th Hui.

38
00:03:14,310 --> 00:03:16,120
Please hold on a little longer!

39
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:17,470
It will be finished soon.

40
00:03:29,470 --> 00:03:31,470
Your Highness, you're so beautiful.

41
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:56,870
Bai Yao, what is this?

42
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,200
Chang'e.

43
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:02,590
Do you want me

44
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:04,800
to be like Chang'e,

45
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:07,280
alone in a cold palace forever?

46
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:08,120
Princess...

47
00:04:10,190 --> 00:04:11,240
Your Highness,

48
00:04:11,470 --> 00:04:13,680
you're the most beautiful in the world,

49
00:04:14,030 --> 00:04:15,360
but also the loneliest.

50
00:04:17,270 --> 00:04:18,110
Yet,

51
00:04:19,190 --> 00:04:20,950
riding the wind to grasp the moon,

52
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:23,950
free of worldly ties.

53
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:28,430
Please enlighten me.

54
00:04:28,870 --> 00:04:30,240
Above the clouds,

55
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,920
is it just lonely and distant?

56
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:41,310
The princess is leaving.

57
00:04:42,750 --> 00:04:43,590
Bai Yao,

58
00:04:44,430 --> 00:04:45,830
can you help me build a palace

59
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:47,600
like in this painting?

60
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:18,390
The Guanghan Palace sketch is finished.

61
00:05:27,950 --> 00:05:29,930
My father has ordered me
to marry into the Huihe.

62
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,390
I'm leaving now.

63
00:07:26,510 --> 00:07:27,350
Bai Yao,

64
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,600
help me build a tomb.

65
00:09:10,390 --> 00:09:11,870
This journey is for nothing again.

66
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,080
Chen.

67
00:09:19,670 --> 00:09:21,720
Chen, are you okay?

68
00:09:24,550 --> 00:09:26,150
I just saw the past

69
00:09:27,750 --> 00:09:29,630
between that princess
and the tomb builder.

70
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:31,360
What?

71
00:09:33,670 --> 00:09:34,870
You didn't see it?

72
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,720
See what?

73
00:09:38,670 --> 00:09:39,670
Were you dreaming?

74
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,270
Is your hand okay?

75
00:09:47,750 --> 00:09:48,600
Piece of cake.

76
00:09:50,670 --> 00:09:52,390
No!

77
00:09:55,030 --> 00:09:56,080
Here.

78
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:58,480
How could this happen?

79
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:13,120
It's just a cenotaph.

80
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,080
Bai Lingling.

81
00:10:22,670 --> 00:10:24,000
Why didn't she resurrect?

82
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:27,150
Why only show me their story?

83
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,000
You saw it too?

84
00:10:35,150 --> 00:10:36,000
Bai Lingling,

85
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:38,670
once the body ceases to function,

86
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:41,120
revival is impossible.

87
00:10:41,790 --> 00:10:43,150
No matter what you saw

88
00:10:43,150 --> 00:10:44,390
or how strong the attachment,

89
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,270
science

90
00:10:46,910 --> 00:10:48,270
can't explain it.

91
00:10:50,150 --> 00:10:51,870
But besides physical death,

92
00:10:52,270 --> 00:10:53,600
there is spiritual death.

93
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:54,840
Beyond that,

94
00:10:55,670 --> 00:10:57,120
there is a final death.

95
00:10:59,630 --> 00:11:00,750
The final one?

96
00:11:02,030 --> 00:11:03,870
It happens when people forget you.

97
00:11:09,030 --> 00:11:11,080
The resurrection Mr. Bai mentioned

98
00:11:11,320 --> 00:11:12,600
may have meant to prove

99
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:14,480
someone still remembers this princess.

100
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:17,550
When some people learned their story,

101
00:11:18,390 --> 00:11:22,000
she'd live on in their hearts.

102
00:11:25,390 --> 00:11:26,230
Miss Bai,

103
00:11:26,550 --> 00:11:28,550
maybe we had a misunderstanding.

104
00:11:28,670 --> 00:11:31,000
At first, I thought
you weren't a good person,

105
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:32,613
but later, seeing your persistence,

106
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:34,480
I really admire you.

107
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:37,720
I'm not good at comforting people,

108
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:40,150
so I'll sing you a song.

109
00:11:42,270 --> 00:11:44,240
♪Dear little sister♪

110
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:45,080
♪Please don't cry♪

111
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:46,270
Alright, alright.

112
00:11:46,280 --> 00:11:47,120
♪Don't♪

113
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:48,200
Enough.

114
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:49,720
That's unbearable.

115
00:11:49,790 --> 00:11:51,360
The meaning is clear.

116
00:11:52,550 --> 00:11:53,390
Miss Bai,

117
00:11:53,510 --> 00:11:54,720
come and visit us sometime.

118
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,480
You can have tea at our little shop.

119
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:59,600
Here's my card.

120
00:12:01,670 --> 00:12:02,510
Well.

121
00:12:03,270 --> 00:12:04,480
As long as you know him,

122
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:05,440
you can find us all.

123
00:12:05,670 --> 00:12:06,510
You can find us all.

124
00:12:12,670 --> 00:12:13,510
Thank you.

125
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:17,800
Take care.

126
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:23,440
Chen Youxi!

127
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:58,120
Seeing the sun makes me so happy.

128
00:13:58,240 --> 00:13:59,840
Back in the daylight.

129
00:14:01,630 --> 00:14:02,870
It feels so good.

130
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:08,270
I've been thinking about it.

131
00:14:08,670 --> 00:14:11,390
What did the tomb builder want?

132
00:14:11,390 --> 00:14:12,270
If I were him,

133
00:14:12,270 --> 00:14:14,120
I'd have eloped with the princess.

134
00:14:14,390 --> 00:14:16,150
Watching a woman he loved

135
00:14:16,150 --> 00:14:17,670
marry someone else

136
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:19,390
is too unmanly.

137
00:14:19,390 --> 00:14:21,360
I just can't understand this.

138
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:29,320
So,

139
00:14:29,390 --> 00:14:31,630
the story teaches us a lesson.

140
00:14:31,630 --> 00:14:32,630
What lesson?

141
00:14:33,030 --> 00:14:35,360
Cherish those around you.

142
00:14:35,440 --> 00:14:38,510
Don't wait until you lose them
to regret it.

143
00:14:45,320 --> 00:14:48,910
Probably, the tomb keeper

144
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:50,150
called the police.

145
00:14:51,270 --> 00:14:52,110
Good.

146
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:54,320
I wondered how to contact Curator Zhu.

147
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:55,390
We can explain,

148
00:14:55,480 --> 00:14:56,320
but Bai Lingling...

149
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:04,080
Though my ancestor's wish
wasn't fulfilled,

150
00:15:04,790 --> 00:15:05,960
thank you all.

151
00:15:06,550 --> 00:15:08,510
We were comrades in adversity.

152
00:15:08,750 --> 00:15:09,960
Can you tell me

153
00:15:10,480 --> 00:15:11,360
if the Lingxiao Pearl

154
00:15:11,360 --> 00:15:12,750
can lift Chen Youxi's curse?

155
00:15:13,790 --> 00:15:14,630
I don't know.

156
00:15:15,390 --> 00:15:16,600
But I can tell you

157
00:15:16,670 --> 00:15:17,630
that the one cursed

158
00:15:17,630 --> 00:15:19,120
like Chen Youxi

159
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:21,080
spends their whole life

160
00:15:21,550 --> 00:15:22,960
searching for the Lingxiao Pearl.

161
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:24,440
And there isn't

162
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:26,213
just one Lingxiao Pearl.

163
00:15:44,496 --> 00:15:45,571
(Police Station)
Director,

164
00:15:45,582 --> 00:15:46,790
most of these criminals

165
00:15:46,910 --> 00:15:48,600
died at the historical site.

166
00:15:48,750 --> 00:15:50,750
Only one female suspect
remains at large.

167
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:52,200
From their criminal actions,

168
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:53,630
we preliminarily believe

169
00:15:53,630 --> 00:15:56,030
they are closely linked

170
00:15:56,030 --> 00:15:57,600
to an international theft gang.

171
00:15:58,150 --> 00:15:59,000
Good.

172
00:15:59,120 --> 00:15:59,960
Keep investigating.

173
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:02,510
Make sure to root out the criminals

174
00:16:02,510 --> 00:16:05,240
to prevent similar relic thefts.

175
00:16:05,390 --> 00:16:06,230
Yes.

176
00:16:07,990 --> 00:16:08,850
Recently,

177
00:16:08,870 --> 00:16:11,200
archaeologists have discovered
a Tang princess's tomb

178
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:13,500
hidden for centuries
in the Yunling Mountains.

179
00:16:13,510 --> 00:16:14,350
As is well known...

180
00:16:14,370 --> 00:16:17,120
Recently, a massive new tomb
has been discovered.

181
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:19,870
Hidden for a thousand years...

182
00:16:19,880 --> 00:16:20,750
They found

183
00:16:20,760 --> 00:16:22,720
a Tang relic site in the mountain.

184
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:24,270
The site is massive.

185
00:16:57,550 --> 00:16:58,550
The mission has failed.

186
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:00,080
I'm sorry.

187
00:17:34,800 --> 00:17:37,900
♪A tiny ark sails;
the sky opens its eyes♪

188
00:17:39,580 --> 00:17:43,260
♪Stillness in motion,
the earth plays its chord♪

189
00:17:44,320 --> 00:17:48,900
♪A leaf falls;
we cross through time and space♪

190
00:17:49,050 --> 00:17:56,050
♪In a blink, all things rest
upon our hands♪

191
00:17:56,610 --> 00:18:07,630
♪La la♪

192
00:18:14,380 --> 00:18:16,370
♪No line divides the border♪

193
00:18:16,810 --> 00:18:19,150
♪Nothing limits your performance♪

194
00:18:19,150 --> 00:18:21,520
♪Everything shows perfect harmony♪

195
00:18:21,520 --> 00:18:24,210
♪Love circles the sky,
the earth, and our faith♪

196
00:18:25,710 --> 00:18:27,420
♪Hey hey hey♪

197
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:30,570
♪Hey hey hey♪

198
00:18:33,220 --> 00:18:34,220
♪Hey hey♪

199
00:18:34,370 --> 00:18:35,370
♪Hey hey♪

200
00:18:36,830 --> 00:18:37,910
♪Hey hey♪

201
00:18:39,540 --> 00:18:43,740
♪Step into the galaxy of colors♪

202
00:18:44,330 --> 00:18:48,040
♪Stars connect our hearts as one♪

203
00:18:50,320 --> 00:18:52,540
♪No difference between you and me♪

204
00:18:52,820 --> 00:18:55,150
♪No lead or side role on this stage♪

205
00:18:55,150 --> 00:18:57,360
♪A perfect life is something we share♪

206
00:18:57,580 --> 00:18:59,860
♪Love declares across the sky and earth♪

207
00:19:00,790 --> 00:19:05,580
♪Huo la yi ya, huo la yi ya♪

208
00:19:05,580 --> 00:19:10,430
♪Time and space go beyond all bounds♪

209
00:19:10,430 --> 00:19:15,280
♪Huo la yi ya, huo la yi ya♪

210
00:19:15,280 --> 00:19:17,370
♪This is our world♪

211
00:19:17,370 --> 00:19:22,400
♪Shining lives bring the change♪

212
00:19:26,930 --> 00:19:29,490
♪In a blink, to forever♪
